n any media whatsoever now known or later invented throughout the world. You hereby disclaim any right to any compensation from JKC in connection with JKC’s exercise of its license rights in and to the User Content you have submitted to JKC. You acknowledge and agree that JKC is under no obligation of confidence to you, and shall not be liable for any use or disclosure of any User Content. By submitting the User Content, you represent and warrant that: (a) you own the copyright in such User Content or that you have a legitimate license to post the User Content, including photographs or other audiovisual material, without any restrictions whatsoever; and/or (b) you have obtained all requisite releases, including likeness releases and automobile owner releases, from all persons whose likeness or automobile is featured or depicted in the User Content.\r\n    </p>\r\n    <p>\r\n        3. JKC reserves the right to review any User Content and remove, delete, redact, or otherwise modify such User Content, in its sole discretion, at any time and from time to time, without notice or further obligation to you. JKC has no obligation to publish, display, or post any User Content. JKC reserves the right to disclose, at any time and from time to time, any information or User Content that JKC deems necessary or appropriate to satisfy any applicable law, regulation, contractual obligation, legal, dispute process, or governmental request.\r\n    </p>', 'User Content', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '51-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-02-09 09:54:04', '2016-02-09 09:54:04', '', 51, 'http://local.jeanknowscars.com/51-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
